---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Testimonials from "../components/Testimonials.astro";
import CallToAction from "../components/CallToAction.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";

const lang = "fr";
---

<Layout
  title="Expérience - Venir sur place"
  description="Séjourner à Pachatopia : immersion nature, prévente de séjours, volontariat, activités agroforestières, et découverte du territoire."
  lang={lang}
>
  <Header lang={lang} />
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Banner -->
    <section class="relative text-white py-24 md:py-32 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0">
        <img src="/images/contacts-hero.webp" alt="" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/80"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-heading font-bold mb-6">Séjourner à Pachatopia</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90">Une expérience au cœur de la nature</p>
      </div>
      <svg class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full" viewBox="0 0 1440 80" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none">
        <path d="M0 40C240 80 480 0 720 40C960 80 1200 0 1440 40V80H0V40Z" fill="white"/>
      </svg>
    </section>

    <!-- Intro with image -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg class="absolute -top-6 right-0 w-64 h-64 opacity-[0.06]" viewBox="0 0 200 200" fill="none">
          <path d="M140 20C140 20 180 60 170 110C160 160 120 180 80 170C40 160 20 120 30 80C40 40 80 20 140 20Z" fill="#0A5B4B"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <p>Au cœur des montagnes de San Carlos en Colombie, Pachatopia souhaite devenir un lieu d'accueil pour les voyageurs, les volontaires et toutes les personnes désireuses de découvrir un mode de vie plus proche de la nature.</p>
            <p>Notre projet est en pleine évolution. Nous travaillons actuellement à la création d'un espace d'accueil qui permettra de partager cette aventure avec des visiteurs du monde entier.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="relative w-full max-w-md overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
              <img src="/images/community.jpg" alt="Communauté Pachatopia" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/20 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Accommodation types -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">Types d'hébergement</h2>
          <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-golden rounded-full mx-auto"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1" style="box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(11,91,75,0.08);">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 21v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h5.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21m0 0h4.5V3.545M12.75 21h7.5V10.75M2.25 21h1.5m18 0h-18M2.25 9l4.5-1.636M18.75 3l-1.5.545m0 6.205l3 1m1.5.5l-1.5-.5M6.75 7.364V3h-3v18m3-13.636l10.5-3.819"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Auberge de jeunesse</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Hébergement convivial pour les voyageurs</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1" style="box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(11,91,75,0.08);">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 12l8.954-8.955c.44-.439 1.152-.439 1.591 0L21.75 12M4.5 9.75v10.125c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125H9.75v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21h4.125c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.75M8.25 21h8.25"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Zone de camping</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Immersion totale dans la nature</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1" style="box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(11,91,75,0.08);">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-earth/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-earth" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8m0 0c-2.5-3-5-5-5-8a5 5 0 0110 0c0 3-2.5 5-5 8z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 21h10"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Éco-lodges</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Logements écologiques et confortables</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Prévente with image -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-center">
          <div class="md:col-span-5">
            <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
              <img src="/images/farm-hero.jpg" alt="Pachatopia séjour" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-7">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-6">Prévente de séjours</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              <p>Pour nous aider à développer ces infrastructures, nous proposons dès aujourd'hui des préventes de séjours à Pachatopia. En réservant votre séjour à l'avance, vous contribuez directement au développement du projet : construction des hébergements, amélioration des infrastructures et plantation d'arbres.</p>
              <p>Ces préventes permettent de soutenir la création d'un lieu qui accueillera à l'avenir des visiteurs souhaitant découvrir la forêt et les réserves naturelles, les plantations de café, les systèmes agroforestiers et la biodiversité exceptionnelle de la région.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Experiences cards -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">Expériences proposées</h2>
          <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-golden rounded-full mx-auto mb-6"></div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Chaque séjour est une occasion de se reconnecter à la nature et de contribuer à un projet porteur de sens.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1" style="box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(11,91,75,0.08);">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8m0 0c-2.5-3-5-5-5-8a5 5 0 0110 0c0 3-2.5 5-5 8z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 21h10"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Plantation d'arbres</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Participez à la régénération des écosystèmes</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1" style="box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(11,91,75,0.08);">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-earth/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-earth" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8C17 8 15 4 12 4C9 4 7 8 7 12C7 16 9 20 12 20C15 20 17 16 17 12"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4C12 4 10 8 10 12C10 16 12 20 12 20"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Découverte du café</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">De la récolte à la tasse, le café agroforestier</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1" style="box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(11,91,75,0.08);">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 006 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 016 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 016-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0018 18a8.967 8.967 0 00-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Initiation à l'agroforesterie</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Apprendre les systèmes de culture régénératifs</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1" style="box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(11,91,75,0.08);">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1115 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Randonnées</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Exploration de la forêt et des montagnes</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1" style="box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(11,91,75,0.08);">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-earth/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-earth" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8.25v-1.5m0 1.5c-1.355 0-2.697.056-4.024.166C6.845 8.51 6 9.473 6 10.608v2.513m6-4.87c1.355 0 2.697.055 4.024.165C17.155 8.51 18 9.473 18 10.608v2.513m-3-4.87v-1.5m-6 1.5v-1.5m12 9.75l-1.5.75a3.354 3.354 0 01-3 0 3.354 3.354 0 00-3 0 3.354 3.354 0 01-3 0 3.354 3.354 0 00-3 0 3.354 3.354 0 01-3 0L3 16.5m15-3.38a48.474 48.474 0 00-6-.37c-2.032 0-4.034.126-6 .37m12 0c.39.049.777.102 1.163.16 1.07.16 1.837 1.094 1.837 2.175v5.17c0 .62-.504 1.124-1.125 1.124H4.125A1.125 1.125 0 013 20.625v-5.17c0-1.08.768-2.014 1.837-2.174A47.78 47.78 0 016 13.12M12.265 3.11a.375.375 0 11-.53 0L12 2.845l.265.265z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-2">Cuisine locale</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Découverte des saveurs de la région</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Restaurant with image -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-center">
          <div class="md:col-span-7">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-6">Restaurant et produits locaux</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              <p>Nous travaillons également à l'ouverture d'un restaurant à Pachatopia, où seront proposés des plats préparés avec les produits cultivés sur place et ceux des agriculteurs de la région.</p>
              <p>Ce lieu permettra de valoriser les produits agricoles locaux, le café du projet, et une cuisine simple, saine et inspirée du territoire.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-5">
            <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
              <img src="/images/agriculture-durable.webp" alt="Produits locaux" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Support quote -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-10 md:p-14 border-l-4 border-accent">
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed italic">En réservant un séjour à Pachatopia, vous ne venez pas seulement passer quelques jours dans un lieu exceptionnel. Vous participez à la création d'un projet qui cherche à régénérer les écosystèmes, soutenir les communautés locales et promouvoir une relation plus harmonieuse avec la nature.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Volunteer stays -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white" id="volontariat">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">Séjours & volontariat</h2>
          <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-golden rounded-full mx-auto mb-6"></div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Préventes de séjours — les visiteurs deviennent des soutiens financiers, des ambassadeurs du projet et de futurs clients du café.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1" style="box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(11,91,75,0.06);">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.036 12.322a1.012 1.012 0 010-.639C3.423 7.51 7.36 4.5 12 4.5c4.638 0 8.573 3.007 9.963 7.178.07.207.07.431 0 .639C20.577 16.49 16.64 19.5 12 19.5c-4.638 0-8.573-3.007-9.963-7.178z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary">Séjour Découverte</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">3 jours — visite du projet, forêt, café.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1" style="box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(11,91,75,0.06);">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8m0 0c-2.5-3-5-5-5-8a5 5 0 0110 0c0 3-2.5 5-5 8z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 21h10"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary">Immersion Agroforestière</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">1 semaine — participation aux plantations et ateliers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1" style="box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(11,91,75,0.06);">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-earth/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-earth" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8C17 8 15 4 12 4C9 4 7 8 7 12C7 16 9 20 12 20C15 20 17 16 17 12"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4C12 4 10 8 10 12C10 16 12 20 12 20"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary">Expérience Café</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">3–5 jours — récolte et transformation du café.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1" style="box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(11,91,75,0.06);">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-primary">Retraite Nature</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">1 semaine — connexion à la nature, marche, permaculture.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mt-10">
          <a href="/comment-participer/" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-golden text-primary font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-golden-dark hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-golden/25">
            <span>Participer au projet</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <Testimonials lang={lang} />
    <CallToAction lang={lang} />
  </main>
  <Footer lang={lang} />
</Layout>
